### ============================================
### 🧪 TEST QR LOGS API - SuperMarketMini
### ============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@adminToken = 
@managerToken = 
@cashierToken = 

### ============================================
### 🔐 1. LOGIN (Chạy trước để lấy token)
### ============================================

### 1.1 Login Admin
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

### 1.2 Login Manager
# @name loginManager
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "manager",
  "password": "Manager@123"
}

### 1.3 Login Cashier
# @name loginCashier
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "cashier",
  "password": "Cashier@123"
}

### ============================================
### 📋 2. GET ALL QR LOGS
### ============================================

### 2.1 Admin - Get All QR Logs (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/qrlogs
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.2 Admin - Get QR Logs with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/qrlogs?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.3 Admin - Filter by Account
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/qrlogs?accountId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.4 Admin - Filter by User
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/qrlogs?userId=3
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.5 Admin - Filter by Confirmation Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/qrlogs?isConfirmed=true
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.6 Admin - Filter by Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/qrlogs?fromDate=2024-01-01&toDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.7 Cashier - Get QR Logs (chỉ thấy của mình) (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/qrlogs
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

### 2.8 No Token - Get QR Logs (Expected: 401 Unauthorized)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/qrlogs

### ============================================
### 🔍 3. GET QR LOG BY ID
### ============================================

### 3.1 Admin - Get QR Log by ID (Expected: 200 OK or 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/qrlogs/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 3.2 Cashier - Get Own QR Log (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/qrlogs/1
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

### 3.3 Cashier - Get Other's QR Log (Expected: 403 Forbidden)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/qrlogs/2
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

### 3.4 Admin - Get Non-existent QR Log (Expected: 404 Not Found)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/qrlogs/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### ✅ 4. CONFIRM QR PAYMENT
### ============================================

### 4.1 Admin - Confirm QR Payment (Expected: 200 OK)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/qrlogs/1/confirm
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "referenceCode": "VCB123456789",
  "note": "Đã xác nhận nhận tiền"
}

### 4.2 Manager - Confirm QR Payment (Expected: 200 OK)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/qrlogs/2/confirm
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

{
  "referenceCode": "TCB987654321",
  "note": "Xác nhận thanh toán"
}

### 4.3 Cashier - Confirm QR Payment (Expected: 200 OK)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/qrlogs/3/confirm
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

{
  "referenceCode": "VTB456789123",
  "note": "Khách đã chuyển khoản"
}

### 4.4 Admin - Confirm Non-existent QR Log (Expected: 404 Not Found)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/qrlogs/99999/confirm
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "referenceCode": "TEST123"
}

### ============================================
### 📊 5. STATISTICS BY ACCOUNT
### ============================================

### 5.1 Admin - Statistics by Account (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/qrlogs/statistics/by-account
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 5.2 Admin - Statistics by Account with Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/qrlogs/statistics/by-account?fromDate=2024-01-01&toDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 5.3 Manager - Statistics by Account (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/qrlogs/statistics/by-account
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### 5.4 Cashier - Statistics by Account (Expected: 403 Forbidden)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/qrlogs/statistics/by-account
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

### ============================================
### 👤 6. STATISTICS BY USER
### ============================================

### 6.1 Admin - Statistics by User (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/qrlogs/statistics/by-user
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6.2 Admin - Statistics by User with Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/qrlogs/statistics/by-user?fromDate=2024-01-01&toDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6.3 Manager - Statistics by User (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/qrlogs/statistics/by-user
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### 6.4 Cashier - Statistics by User (Expected: 403 Forbidden)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/qrlogs/statistics/by-user
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

### ============================================
### 📝 HƯỚNG DẪN SỬ DỤNG
### ============================================
### 
### 1. Cài đặt VS Code extension "REST Client"
### 2. Chạy các request Login đầu tiên để lấy token
### 3. Copy token vào biến tương ứng
### 4. Chạy các request test theo thứ tự
###
